    "updated_at": "2016-05-14T11:27:06Z",
    "body": "Unfortunately Chromium doesn't implement video acceleration for the hardware used by Raspberry Pi, I would like to fix this, but the work would be really huge, and none of us in Electron actually knows how to do that.\n\nI suggest opening an issue at Chromium's [issues list](https://crbug.com) instead, I'm closing this since it is an upstream issue, and we are not able to fix it on Electron's side.\n"
